### Browser Installation Configuration - Playwright CI

Source: https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/blob/main/docs/src/release-notes-js.md

Configure browser installation in CI environments using npm and Playwright CLI commands. Ensures browsers are explicitly downloaded after dependency installation since Playwright v1.38 no longer downloads browsers automatically during npm install.

```yaml
- run: npm ci
- run: npx playwright install --with-deps
```

