### Create Global Setup Test File with Database Initialization

Source: https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/blob/main/docs/src/test-global-setup-teardown-js.md

Implements a global setup test that runs before dependent projects. The setup function is defined as a regular test using the test() function and performs initialization tasks like creating a new database.

```javascript
import { test as setup } from '@playwright/test';

setup('create new database', async ({ }) => {
  console.log('creating new database...');
  // Initialize the database
});
```

