### Configure Playwright Global Setup

Source: https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/blob/main/docs/src/test-api/class-testconfig.md

Sets the path to a global setup file. This file will be executed once before all tests, requiring it to export a function that accepts a `FullConfig` argument. An array of paths can be provided for multiple setup files.

```javascript
import { defineConfig } from '@playwright/test';

export default defineConfig({
  globalSetup: './global-setup',
});
```

