### Playwright Test Using Pre-authenticated State (TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/blob/main/docs/src/test-global-setup-teardown-js.md

This test file demonstrates how a Playwright test can directly access a page assuming the user is already authenticated. This is possible because the `storageState` option in the configuration file is populated by the global setup.

```typescript
import { test } from '@playwright/test';

test('test', async ({ page }) => {
  await page.goto('/');
  // You are signed in!
});
```

