### Configure Playwright to bundle drivers for all platforms (XML)

Source: https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/blob/main/docs/src/library-csharp.md

This XML snippet shows how to modify the project file (`.csproj`) to instruct Playwright to bundle browser drivers for all supported platforms, overriding the default behavior of bundling only for the target runtime.

```xml
<PropertyGroup>
