### Configure Playwright to bundle drivers for specific platforms (XML)

Source: https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/blob/main/docs/src/library-csharp.md

This XML snippet demonstrates how to specify a semicolon-separated list of platforms (e.g., `osx`, `linux`) for which Playwright should bundle browser drivers in the project file, allowing selective inclusion.

