### Define Global Base URL in Playwright Configuration

Source: https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/blob/main/docs/src/test-fixtures-js.md

This Playwright configuration snippet shows how to establish a global `baseURL` that will be applied to all tests by default. This base URL can then be selectively overridden or completely unset within individual test files or describe blocks. It provides a common starting point for test navigation.

```js
import { defineConfig } from '@playwright/test';

export default defineConfig({
  use: {
    baseURL: 'https://playwright.dev',
